problems.title: Number of Different Subsequences GCDs (Number Theory)
problems.description:
You are given an array nums that consists of positive integers.
Return the number of different GCDs among all non-empty subsequences of nums.

Input Format:
First line: integer n.
Second line: n space-separated integers.

Output Format:
Print a single integer: the count.
hintsList: Iterate all possible GCD values from 1 to max(nums).
For each value g, check if it can be formed as GCD of its multiples present in nums.
